        {
            "title": "量化派高收88.78% 每手賬賺4350元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">羊小咩母公司量化派(02685)股份今日掛牌，以18.5元收市，較招股價9.8元高88.78%；以1手500股計，認購並獲配每手賬面賺4350元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"量化派招股書封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/02685.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"量化派招股書封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/02685.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">量化派招股書封面</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該股今早高開1.65倍，以26元開市，初段一度衝上27.8元，較招股價高1.84倍，其後升幅迅速收窄，但全日低位18.3元仍較招股價高86.73%；成交1.27億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15461833-%e9%87%8f%e5%8c%96%e6%b4%be%e9%ab%98%e6%94%b688-78-%e6%af%8f%e6%89%8b%e8%b3%ac%e8%b3%ba4350%e5%85%83",
